snippet.title: Catalyst Wake Trailer
snippet.description:
PLAY THE DEMO!
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1661470/The_Evolving_World_Catalyst_Wake_Demo/

itch.io: https://lockedon.itch.io/tewcw


Only 3000 humans remain after three apocalyptic events, referred to as the "Catalysts", severely decreased the population. Catalyst One resulted in the air being toxic to breathe, so everyone wears masks. After the collapse of the government, various organizations have formed, and fight each other for territory and resources.

Credits:

LockedOn - Developer
OddTillTheEnd - Composer
Anjali Kunapaneni - Casting/Voice Director
A.J. Beckles As Oliver Naut
Gianni Matragrano As Namo
Ashely Biski As Nihility
Jason Marnocha As Sawbones
Liz Morey As Mistslayer
Sean Chiplock As Miles
Su Ling Chan As Wisher
Edwyn Tiong As Oxlo
Alex Bankier As Grimalkin
Ivy Dupler As Sabbatical
Phillip Sacramento As Roth
David J. Dixon As Arrdo
Allen Winter As Axis
